==English==

===Etymology===
A contraction of [[some more]], so called because they’re meant to be so tasty you always want some more.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/s̩ ˈmɔːr/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔː(r)|-ɔː(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{US}} A snack food made by combining [[graham]] crackers, [[marshmallow]]s (frequently toasted) and [[chocolate]], a typical camping fireside treat.

